    "description": "AI now writes 90% of our code.\n(Yes, really...)\n\nBiggest shift:\nWe skip designing & prototyping.\n\n⛔ How we used to do it:\n- Plan a new feature.\n- Draft the design in Figma.\n- Prototype it in Figma.\n- Hand it over to a developer.\n- Developer manually codes it.\n\n✨ How we do it now:\n- Vibe coding directly in Lovable.\n\n✅ Result:\nPlanning, drafting, designing & prototyping ALL happen in one single place. And the artifact is REAL application code, not just a slideshow.\n\nDon't let people tell you AI can't code.\nIt can. Let me show you.",
